user.bio:
Since first picking up a camera, I have been in love with creating and telling stories. Currently I am making ads for companies such as the YMCA and Chicanos por la Causa. I hope, however, to be able to delve into the creative side of film further into the future. My website is:

Gutiproductions.com

If anyone in Phoenix is looking for a video, don't hesitate to contact me.
